snippet.title: Ariana Grande Kisses Miley Cyrus at MTV VMA 2014 - MTV Video Music Awards 2014

localized.description:
Ariana Grande Kisses Miley Cyrus at MTV VMA 2014 - MTV Video Music Awards 2014

Ariana Grande & Miley Cyrus at MTV VMA 2014

Ariana Grande & Miley Cyrus Spotted Cozying & Enjoying together. 

The VMAs have so many stars, it's no wonder new collaborations start there!

And here's a couple stars coming together now! It's Ariana Grande and Miley Cyrus!

And PDA to boot!

We hope Ariana Grande didn't expect more of a kiss than that! Doesn't she know where that tongue has been?

Yes, the famous words of Katy Perry after Miley and the smooched at Miley's Bangerz Tour.

Luckily for Ariana Grande, it was just a kiss and there was no tongue action involved.

Guess Ariana knows where that tongue has been. EVERYWHERE!

LOL!

So what do you guys think about the MTV VMA 2014?

Are you satisfied with all the winners and performances or you were looking forward to something controversial this year too?

Drop in your comments to let us know. Thumbs up for Ariana Grande and a decent Miley Cryus at the MTV VMAs and don't forget to subscribe to HollywoodCIA
